title: The Autopsy of Jane Doe
review: The first half had me interested but I really went off it when they started to rely too much on loud jump scares, sometimes even with pop-up scary faces. There is a completely worthless emotional scene about someone who shows up dead and there is slow sad music, and the characters just continue on like nothing happened, like they could have moved that scene to any point and it would have been the same because it has no effect. It ends dumbly.
